A Trowel,
 from the Fr. G. Truelle; or the Belg. Troweel, idem;
 all from the Lat. Trulla, idem.

Trum, in Cards,
 from the Fr. G. Triomphe, the Ital. Trionfo, or the Belg. and Teut. Trumpff, idem;
 all from the Lat. Triumphus, idem.

A VAil,
 from the Fr. G. Voile, or the Belg. Witle, Wiele, idem;
 all from the Lat. Velum, idem; this from the Lat. Velo, to cover.

